* Every little movement *

40:22.654 --> 40:26.758
* Every motion
of your hips *

40:26.758 --> 40:29.895
* I feel the compulsion *

40:29.895 --> 40:35.433
* To pull you
to my sweet lips *

40:35.433 --> 40:39.304
* Is it a black magic spell *

40:39.304 --> 40:41.172
* You put me under? *

40:42.841 --> 40:46.545
* This miracle moment *

40:46.545 --> 40:50.549
* Never let it end *

40:50.549 --> 40:54.586
* Every little movement *

40:54.586 --> 40:58.657
* Is beyond improvement *

40:58.657 --> 41:01.527
* You are the magician *

41:01.527 --> 41:06.765
* I've been wishing for
forever *

